cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper deals with person re-identification using depth sensors and deep learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel approach for transfer learning, which involves sharing model parameters between RGB and depth data, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also uses reinforcement learning for training temporal attention, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with video data, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.RO (Robotics).
